## Field Ontology Schema

Every field in the knowledge base must have these attributes:

```python
Field:
  id: str
  name: str
  description: str                    # plain language
  subfields: list[Subfield]
  math_level: Literal["Low", "Medium", "High"]
  coding_level: Literal["Low", "Medium", "High"]
  biology_depth: Literal["Low", "Medium", "High"]
  research_orientation: Literal["Low", "Medium", "High"]
  prerequisites: list[str]            # e.g., ["Calculus", "Physics"]
  personality_traits: list[str]       # who fits
  career_paths: list[Career]
  adjacent_fields: list[str]          # field IDs
  salary_range: SalaryRange           # entry/mid/senior
  graduate_school_required: bool
  job_outlook: str                    # BLS growth rate
  day_in_life: str
  misconceptions: list[str]
```

