## Agent Workflows (LangGraph)

### Exploration Agent
1. Embed user interest description
2. Retrieve top-N similar fields from vector store
3. LLM ranks and filters by fit
4. LLM generates match explanations
5. LLM generates 3 clarifying follow-up questions

### Deep Dive Agent
1. Retrieve structured field data from Postgres
2. For each section, either return stored text or call LLM to generate
3. Cache generated explanations back to DB

### Comparison Agent
1. Retrieve structured data for each requested field
2. LLM generates narrative comparison per dimension
3. Return both structured table + narrative summary

### Clarification Agent
1. Parse user preference statement (e.g., "I hate coding")
2. Update user preference profile
3. Re-rank field recommendations

