## API Endpoints

```
POST /api/explore          — interest description → ranked fields
GET  /api/field/{id}       — full deep dive profile
POST /api/compare          — list of field IDs → comparison table
POST /api/clarify          — user preference update → re-ranked fields
GET  /api/fields           — list all available fields (for autocomplete)
```

